      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RITZA WOTTON (1) has a terrific record this track and trip with two wins and one placing from three starts. In the money last time at Angle Park (30.96) in a Grade 5, finishing a 6 length third. Looks suited here and rates on top. BINNAWAY WARRIOR (3) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors four on end. Last start copped a bump in the run and finished third in a Grade 4/5 at Angle Park (31.39). Expected to feature. BIG BOSS GIBLET (5) missed the frame latest but had been racing well prior to that including a Grade 6 win two back (31.42) at this track. Has the ability and expected to do much better. KEELEY ROSE (7) is right in the mix.",
